{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"VRStageParameters","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters\"><code>VRStageParameters</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters/sittingToStandingTransform\"><code>sittingToStandingTransform</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters/sizeX\"><code>sizeX</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters/sizeY\"><code>sizeY</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>WebVR API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/displayId\"><code>Gamepad.displayId</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/activeVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.activeVRDisplays</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.getVRDisplays()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayCapabilities\"><code>VRDisplayCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayEvent\"><code>VRDisplayEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters\"><code>VREyeParameters</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRFieldOfView\"><code>VRFieldOfView</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRFrameData\"><code>VRFrameData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRLayerInit\"><code>VRLayerInit</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRPose\"><code>VRPose</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API</a> の <strong><code>VRStageParameters</code></strong> インターフェイスは，ルームスケール体験に対応しているデバイス用にステージエリアを記述する値を表現しています．</p>\n<p>このインターフェイスには <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/stageParameters\"><code>VRDisplay.stageParameters</code></a> プロパティを通じてアクセスできます．</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"プロパティ","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"vrstageparameters.sittingtostandingtransform\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters/sittingToStandingTransform\"><code>VRStageParameters.sittingToStandingTransform</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/getPose\"><code>VRDisplay.getPose()</code></a>/<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/getImmediatePose\"><code>VRDisplay.getImmediatePose()</code></a> で返される着席(sitting-space)位置を立位(standing-space)位置にするための変換行列を含んでいます．</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vrstageparameters.sizex\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters/sizeX\"><code>VRStageParameters.sizeX</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>プレイエリア境界の幅を返します．単位はメートルです．</em></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vrstageparameters.sizey\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters/sizeY\"><code>VRStageParameters.sizeY</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>プレイエリア境界の奥行きを返します．単位はメートルです．</em></p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">TBD.\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"about:unknown#interface-vrstageparameters\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"ja\">VRStageParameters の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-\">不明</span></td>\n      <td>Initial definition</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.VRStageParameters","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参照","title":"参照","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API homepage</a>.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://mozvr.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MozVr.com</a> — Mozilla VR チームのデモ，ダウンロード，その他のリソース．</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"プロパティ"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性"},{"text":"参照","id":"参照"}],"summary":"WebVR API の VRStageParameters インターフェイスは，ルームスケール体験に対応しているデバイス用にステージエリアを記述する値を表現しています．","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"VRStageParameters","locale":"en-US","native":"Engl